high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Take the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the round brown table in the corner.
Cut the apple on the table into thirds.
Turn left and walk to the oven.
Put the knife in the microwave above the oven.
Turn around and walk back to the round brown table in the corner.
Pick up one piece of the sliced apple from the table.
Turn left and walk to the oven.
Put the apple slice in the microwave above the oven and cook the apple, then remove the apple slice.
Turn around and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the small brown shelf with a tomato on it.
Place the cut apple slice on the brown shelf next to the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, cook a piece of the apple in a microwave, put the apple slice on the brown shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, hang a right and go to the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is in the sink.
Turn around, go to the stove and hang a left, go to the wall, hang a left, go forward to the round table.
Use the knife to cut the apple at the back of the round table.
Back up, turn around, go forward, turn to the right and go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside, close the microwave.
Turn around, go to the door, turn to the left and go to the round table.
Pick up a piece of the apple that has been cut from the table.
Back up, turn around, go forward, turn to the right and go forward to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, turn it on to cook, remove the apple when it is done cooking.
Back up, turn around, go to the door, turn to the right and go to the small black table.
Put the apple on the table to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked apple on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink on the counter.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle in the sink.
Turn to your left and move across the room to the black round table.
Cut the apple on the black table.
Turn left and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the knife inside the microwave.
Turn around and head back to the black round table.
Pick up an apple slice on the black round table.
Head towards the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave and put the apple slice inside the microwave and heat it.
Take the apple slice out of the microwave and carry it to the black square table across the room.
Place the apple slice on the black square table.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple and microwave it.
